## Layer Dependency Diagram (Simplified)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  subgraph layers
    direction TB
    L4["4. Presentation"]
    L3["3. Application"]
    L2["2. Domain"]
    L1["1. Infrastructure"]
  end
  L4 --> L3
  L3 --> L2
  L1 --> L2
  L3 -.->|uses via ports| L1
```

- **Domain (2)** is the core; no outgoing dependencies to other layers.
- **Application (3)** orchestrates use cases and may depend on **Infrastructure (1)** only through interfaces/ports defined in the application or domain.
- **Presentation (4)** exposes the API and depends on Application and Domain.
- **Infrastructure (1)** implements platform-specific logic and depends only on Domain (and optionally on application-defined ports).

